                <h1>Duke researchers anchor in Gulf to study oil spill</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/32388cf1-4a67-431f-9673-89bf1ba9042d.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Duke&#x20;researchers&#x20;set&#x20;sail&#x20;for&#x20;the&#x20;Gulf&#x20;of&#x20;Mexico&#x20;aboard&#x20;The&#x20;Cape&#x20;Hatteras&#x20;June&#x20;5.&#x20;&#x20;Working&#x20;jointly&#x20;with&#x20;researchers&#x20;from&#x20;across&#x20;the&#x20;country,&#x20;the&#x20;team&#x20;plans&#x20;to&#x20;study&#x20;the&#x20;effects&#x20;and&#x20;potential&#x20;damage&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;oil&#x20;spill." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Duke researchers set sail for the Gulf of Mexico aboard The Cape Hatteras June 5.  Working jointly with researchers from across the country, the team plans to study the effects and potential damage of the oil spill.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/scott-taylor-special-to-the-chronicle">Scott Taylor/ Special to The Chronicle</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/tullia-rushton">Tullia Rushton</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">June 10, 2010 | 12:00am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
